&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This role would require a hybrid schedule in our Calgary office (Tues-Thur in office, Mon/Fri work from home).&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
